Happy Joe Isitua popularly known as Waka About is set to debut ‘LEADERSHIP WEEKEND EDUTAINMENT, a potpourri of education and entertainment news, for reading pleasure of our esteemed readers. The two-page column, which will be part of the regular features of LEADERSHIP Weekend with effect from tomorrow.  It will be a blend of pidgin and English. Speaking on the page, Isitua said, “The whole idea is to help people enjoy their weekend by giving them soft news that they can read in a relax atmosphere.” Catch up with Waka About every Saturday by getting a copy of LEADERSHIP.